<br>
-not everyone does that.<br>
-All those regular mantinence requests? i.e. 20k service, 40k, 44k, 50k, 60k, et all?  The rental place hits those religiously.<br>
-They can't send out a car with a broken doodad, so into the shop it goes.  And every shop i've ever been in has always done the &quot;well, we fixed X, but while we were taking Y and Z off to get to X, we found that Y's getting a little worn, and that you've plum lost the bolts that are supposed to hold Q on.  So we fixed Q, and you should really deal with Y in the next couple of months.&quot;<br>
-Most of these get a vacuuming once a week, in addition to the vac/wash they get after being brought back by a client.  The interiors are kept clean. <p>Ninen of Saryrn<br>
